@host = http://localhost:5080

### Health / index
GET {{host}}/

### Search products (Elasticsearch + Redis cache-aside)
GET {{host}}/catalog/products/search?q=laptop

### Fuzzy search (typo tolerated by ES fuzziness)
GET {{host}}/catalog/products/search?q=keybord

### Index a new product
POST {{host}}/catalog/products
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "USB-C Hub",
  "description": "7-in-1 USB-C hub with HDMI and ethernet",
  "category": "Accessories",
  "price": 59,
  "tags": ["usb-c", "hub", "developer"]
}

### Place an order that SUCCEEDS (stock available) -> saga completes it
# productId values match the seeded stock/catalog.
POST {{host}}/orders
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "customerName": "Acme Corp",
  "lines": [
    { "productId": "11111111-0000-0000-0000-000000000001", "productName": "Pro Laptop 16", "quantity": 2, "unitPrice": 2499 },
    { "productId": "11111111-0000-0000-0000-000000000002", "productName": "Wireless Mouse", "quantity": 2, "unitPrice": 39 }
  ]
}

### Place an order that FAILS stock (only 3 desks in stock) -> saga COMPENSATES (cancels)
POST {{host}}/orders
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "customerName": "Bulk Buyer",
  "lines": [
    { "productId": "11111111-0000-0000-0000-000000000003", "productName": "Standing Desk", "quantity": 99, "unitPrice": 599 }
  ]
}

### Get an order by id (replace with the id returned above). Status -> Completed or Cancelled.
GET {{host}}/orders/REPLACE_WITH_ORDER_ID

### Inventory levels (watch QuantityReserved change)
GET {{host}}/inventory/stock

### Shipments (created for successful orders)
GET {{host}}/shipping/shipments
